fields.name: Custom Name Keychain
fields.description: Beautiful resin keychain with your custom name or text. Perfect for personal use or as a gift. Each piece is handcrafted with high-quality resin and comes with a sturdy keyring.

fields.name: Photo Resin Keychain
fields.description: Preserve your precious memories in a beautiful resin keychain. Upload your favorite photo and we'll create a stunning keepsake that you can carry everywhere.

fields.name: Premium Photo + Text Keychain
fields.description: The ultimate personalized keychain combining your favorite photo with custom text. Perfect for couples, families, or special occasions. Premium quality resin with crystal-clear finish.

fields.name: Quote Resin Bookmark
fields.description: Elegant resin bookmark with your favorite quote or motivational text. Perfect for book lovers and students. Durable and beautiful design that won't damage your books.

fields.name: Memory Photo Frame
fields.description: Small resin photo frame perfect for desk or shelf display. Upload your favorite photo and we'll create a beautiful mini frame that captures your special moments.

fields.name: Custom Resin Magnet Set
fields.description: Set of 3 custom resin magnets with your photos and text. Perfect for refrigerator decoration or office use. Strong magnets with beautiful resin finish.
